timelineItems.name: Burgundy Wave
timelineItems.text: In case you were wondering just how bad the #Rapids96 defense was, getting scored on by Atiba Harris is a pretty good indicator

timelineItems.comment: Second Half ends, Colorado Rapids 1, San Jose Earthquakes 1.
